{"tid":448642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（公投）有無巴打一個人食哂得金拱門既18件麥樂雞餐？","createTime":"2017-10-26T11:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T13:53:17.000Z","uid":5812,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f86b2735a98882cfbdb7f1015e8474171be4d7e2","tid":448642,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:37:31.000Z","msg":"真係好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加埋大再加sharkshark粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/193711_71259fb7da103adc25fd43024fcd57cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F193711_71259fb7da103adc25fd43024fcd57cb.jpg&h=19801558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dffdceb3765a0e3185b5519adfd1c1231a63b1","tid":448642,"uid":155199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"18 件小意思。 係美國的時候，我一條友食個魚柳飽加20 件。 最高記錄40 件加個飽。"},{"pid":"09d28f4819ecc195c17a7f8a93f82e13083b2145","tid":448642,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>18 件小意思。 係美國的時候，我一條友食個魚柳飽加20 件。 最高記錄40 件加個飽。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d512f09aa6565aae77d606325a6c0a0b92f109cf","tid":448642,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"欣宜食得哂"},{"pid":"3ab327f3f3ff6261799c38df354fc267fcda3f21","tid":448642,"uid":63845,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:53:17.000Z","msg":"一個二個開埋晒啲<br />\n認同A觀點就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認同B觀點就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你問我，呢班人係咪真心熱愛投選運動而做呢種事，以我觀察黎睇，好明顯唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就等我抽樣搵少少例子<br />\n<br />\n[二選一] 靜靜雞 定 靜雞雞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/445235\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/445235</a><br />\n呢類就最為垃圾既，乜柒都無直接彈兩行野叫人投，不過呢個post就天有眼，無人理佢，抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n揸車嘅你地 會唔會讓斑馬線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/439945\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/439945</a><br />\n同上，都係果啲引人望完個正負就會輕易有答案既垃圾post，而呢個更加有幾百人投添，無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[有圖]係火車無啦啦有條女係我張床<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/445123\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/445123</a><br />\n呢個相對黎講已經算好啲，本來一路都有圖有字，但好可惜條友最後都係屎忽痕要整返個投票調查，而好明顯個風向都實係吹向佢set做正評果個option架啦，結果又成為一個make到noise上熱門既廢post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過有好就當然會有更加廢既，而最令人覺得肉酸既係呢類post誇起上黎往往係可以比人煲到上千even數千正評，咁我一開頭就話係心理唔平衡既人為呃正評先會開呢類post<br />\n<br />\n不過由我一路打呢篇野一路搵資料啦<br />\n我發現如果話晒佢地係心理唔平衡而咁做，的確係太過主觀有欠公允，所以我又得出左另一個原因<br />\n就係呢類人表達能力極度有問題，佢地唔開呢類正負評post就無辦法進行正常既討論，如果你講野mean啲，直頭可以稱呢類人係智障都完全無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁當然無論以上人士係心理唔平衡又好定表達能力有缺撼都好，我都會建議佢地立即就醫，唔好再沉溺連登損人不利己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實搞公投，舉行投選活動就無罪既，但如果係濫用左就當然唔可取，呢啲人開埋晒呢啲問東問西或者係邊條女正啲既post，好啦問完之後又有咩用呢，任何投選投票都一定有佢自身既出發點，如果投完之後根本無下文無用處既，唔單止浪費資源，仲對真心熱愛投票活動既朋友仔都好唔公平，因為真係令投票既本質改變晒，搞到低質晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁成日開無聊投票既低質會員睇到呢度，以後仲會唔會咁做？希望你呢啲垃圾識諗喇快啲收手喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}